  <p>Creates a new timeout source.</p>  <p>The source will not initially be associated with any <link xref="GLib.MainContext"/>
and must be added to one with <link xref="GLib.Source.attach"/> before it will be
executed.</p>  <p>The scheduling granularity/accuracy of this timeout source will be
in seconds.</p>  <p>The interval given in terms of monotonic time, not wall clock time.
See <link xref="GLib.get_monotonic_time"/>.</p>
  <p>Since 2.14</p>
